claim.claim-text:
A zip fastener comprising:
opposing and mutually engagable rows of zip teeth each mounted upon a respective stringer tape;
a slider, movably mounted upon the teeth, being movable forwards along the teeth to cause interdigitation of the teeth thereby to fasten the zip and movable backwards to cause extradigitation and unfastening of the zip;
a docking member, engagable with a front end of the slider in a manner which creates a seal between the slider and the docking member.
